+### Rust idioms Violated
+
+- **No `unsafe` blocks** — Clean
+- **No `unwrap()` in production** — Clean
+- **No `as any`** — Clean (verified no suppressed warnings)
+- **No `@ts-ignore` equivalents** — N/A (Rust)
